features: Enjoy premium video quality with the Logitech C920S Pro HD Webcam. Designed for full HD 1080P video calls, this webcam offers a professional experience that makes you stand out. Whether you're on a business call, streaming, or just catching up with loved ones, the C920S ensures you're seen in the best light. It's compatible with PC, laptop, and Mac, making it a versatile choice for all your video needs. Plus, it comes with a built-in microphone for clear, crisp audio.

Experience superior video quality with the Logitech C920S Pro HD Webcam. It features a high-definition glass lens that ensures your videos are recorded in full HD 1080P resolution, delivering crisp and vibrant visuals. Whether you're using it for video calls on your PC or laptop, streaming content, or recording videos, this webcam offers exceptional clarity and detail. Plus, it comes with a built-in microphone for clear audio.

HD Autofocus and Light Correction - The Logitech C920S Pro HD Webcam offers a high-definition video experience with its advanced autofocus and light correction features. This ensures a razor-sharp image quality in every environment, making it ideal for use as a webcam for PC, laptop, or desktop computer. Whether you're video conferencing, streaming, or recording, this camera adjusts to your lighting conditions to produce bright, contrasted images.

Experience superior sound quality during video calls and recordings, thanks to the stereo audio with dual microphones on the Logitech C920S Pro HD Webcam. This feature captures natural, clear sound, enhancing your communication whether you're in a professional meeting, catching up with friends, or streaming content online. Ideal for users seeking a high-quality webcam for PC, laptop, or desktop computer. Compatible with various operating systems including Windows 11 and Mac.

Equipped with a privacy shutter, this Logitech C920S Pro HD Webcam puts you in control of what you show, ensuring your privacy and protecting the lens with a snugly fitting cover. Ideal for both professional and casual users, it delivers sharp, clear images with 1080p resolution, making it a top choice for video calls, streaming, and recording. Whether you're connecting with loved ones or conducting a business meeting, this webcam ensures a seamless and high-quality experience.
body.description: This pre-owned or refurbished product has been professionally inspected and tested to work and look like new. How a product becomes part of Amazon Renewed, your destination for pre-owned, refurbished products: A customer buys a new product and returns it or trades it in for a newer or different model. That product is inspected and tested to work and look like new by Amazon-qualified suppliers. Then, the product is sold as an Amazon Renewed product on Amazon. If not satisfied with the purchase, renewed products are eligible for replacement or refund under the Amazon Renewed Guarantee.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to get a refurbished model because it’s a backup in case my primary camera stops working. Since I work remote, I sit on video calls most of my day and having a working video camera is a must. This works perfectly; plug and play just like my existing camera. So glad to have a backup camera at a reasonable price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This great WebCam easily fits on top of my laptop and produces a much higher quality image of me and I look so much better in online meetings. I purchased this WebCam twice for my two different work locations. I like the privacy flip shield as well when I want to be sure no one can accidentally see me on camera when I don’t want to.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Plug and play
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for these days of working from home when you have video meetings. The blue light to indicate it is on is nice, and the physical shield is tops. The video quality is great, I need all the help I can get to look good in these meetings. I'm often if not always the best quality picture in the video meetings I am in.Plugged in to my Windows 10 laptop and it was found, installed and made available to my video room software.If I had to complain, it would be the mount is a tiny bit larger then the bezel of my monitor, so it covers up some of the title bar of my window.

reviews.reviewText: ordered as renewed. Works perfectly. But the camera doesn't move on a pivot point, you cant change the side to side angle of the picture if you mount the camera on top of a monitor.Heck, my old Logitech camera that was at least 10 years old swiveled. I thought that this was a given.Other than that its fine. only 4 stars though because of the design defect. Unless it is supposed to swivel and the renewed people put a different mount on it.
